  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA81">
<l>pakalirā veṉpatuvum pāviyā temmai</l>
<l>yikalcey tirupoḻutu māḷvar takavāt</l>
<l>toḻumparivar cīrkkun tuṇaiyila reṉṟōrār</l>
<l>ceḻumparavai mēyār terintu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without regarding whether it is day [or] night he will</l>
<l>with hostility rule us both times, he will not consider</l>
<l>that these are unfit slaves, without support because of excellence,</l>
<l>the resident of the ample expanse, understandingly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
